      <div xml:id="Aink25-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink25">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> ayalpuṟan tanta puṉiṟṟuvaḷar paiṅkāy</l>
          <l> vayalaic ceṅkoṭi kaḷva ṉaṟukkuṅ</l>
          <l> kaḻaṉi yūraṉ mārpupalark</l>
          <l> kiḻainekiḻ cella lāku maṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> The chest of the man from the village of paddy fields</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> where crabs tear off the red creepers of the purslane</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> [and] the neighbourhood protects the new-born, fresh unripe-fruit as it
            grows </l>
          <l> Is [the reason] that the jewels of many [girls] become loose [and] go, mother.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
